gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 127, Trail Blazers 112
gameRecap.excerpt: The Denver Nuggets defeated the Portland Trail Blazers, 127-112. Michael Porter Jr. (34 points, 12 rebounds) and Nikola Jokic (29 points on 12-17 FG, 15 rebounds, 14 assists) led the Nuggets as Jerami Grant (25 points) and Deandre Ayton (22 points, 10 rebounds) led Portland in the loss. The Nuggets improve to 38-19 as the Blazers move to 15-40.
